Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.08,0:02:34.46,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Day and night
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.96,0:02:37.63,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}We searched along the rails
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.63,0:02:40.72,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Hoping to find another trail
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.93,0:02:42.43,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Leading to heaven
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.43,0:02:45.01,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}The heavens are waiting for motion
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.01,0:02:47.72,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Fired up for action
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.72,0:02:48.85,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}There's no gain
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.85,0:02:49.60,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Only pain
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.60,0:02:50.44,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Only pain
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.44,0:02:51.14,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Only pain
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.14,0:02:51.90,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Only pain
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.90,0:02:52.73,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}All this pain
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.73,0:02:54.90,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}My pains don't exist to entertain
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.90,0:02:57.32,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Count with me, one two three
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.32,0:03:00.74,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}How many liters can you bleed?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.15,0:03:04.53,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}How many turns you plan to last?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.53,0:03:07.08,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}How many lives you need?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.54,0:03:09.37,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}I saw a star
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.37,0:03:12.58,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Brightening up the dark
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.83,0:03:21.43,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}So don't you stop my fires from burning our everything
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.43,0:03:26.31,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}You and me are nothing but temporary
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.31,0:03:31.60,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Don't you start begging for mercy
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.60,0:03:33.10,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}For when I win
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.10,0:03:34.86,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}I won't forgive
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.86,0:03:36.40,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}And I shall win
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.40,0:03:37.94,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}And I shall win
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.94,0:03:44.70,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Yes, I shall win your one-sided game
